%F A396326 Equals 1/(Gamma(1/2+i)*Gamma(1/2-i)) = 1/abs(Gamma(1/2+i))^2, where i is the imaginary unit.
%F A396326 Equals lim_{n->oo} n * Product_{m=1..n} (1 - 1/m + 5/(4*m^2)).
